--------------------------------------------------------------------------
The following material was ADDED or MODIFIED for educational purposes by
the radiosonda_PIcaro contributors. These additions are distributed under
the same Clear BSD License and do not alter the copyright of the original
Semtech code.

Added:
  - specs/exercises/         Six self-contained didactic exercises (00-06),
                             with ChirpStack provisioning/consumption scripts.
  - specs/bmp280-gnss-tracker/  BMP280 + GNSS tracker specs, pinout, guides.
  - specs/demos/            Flashing and API-registration guides.
  - wiki/                   LoRa/LoRaWAN teaching material.
  - BMP280 sensor driver and I2C HAL for STM32L4 (added to the geolocation
    application and the smtc_hal_l4 layer).
  - Arduino/LMIC TTGO ESP32 (SX1276) node sketches (third-party node).

